---

<section
    id="rutina"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-overflow-hidden wheat-grinding"
>
    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-opacity-10 wheat-pointer-events-none wheat-grinding-bg">
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
        <div class="wheat-grinding-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--narrow wheat-text-center wheat-relative wheat-grinding-content">
        <div class="wheat-space-y-6 wheat-space-y-8@md">
            <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-grinding-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase">
                La Rutina
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-4xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-grinding-title">El amanecer del dolor</h2>
            <div class="wheat-space-y-4 wheat-space-y-6@md wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-grinding-desc wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto">
                <p>
                    El trigo exigía ser molido. No podíamos comerlo crudo. Así que inventamos la
                    piedra de moler.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Y con ella, inventamos el dolor de espalda crónico, la artritis en las rodillas
                    y las hernias. Durante horas, cada día, arrodillados, empujando una piedra
                    contra otra.
                </p>
                <p>El cuerpo humano, diseñado para trepar y correr, se rompió contra el suelo.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-grinding {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-grinding-bg {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .wheat-grinding-line {
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-grinding-content {
        z-index: 10;
    }
    .wheat-grinding-chapter {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-grinding-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-grinding-desc {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-space-y-8\@md > * + * {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .wheat-space-y-6\@md > * + * {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
